rning and traditional numerical\napproaches in tandem to reduce computational complexity accelerate scientific\ndiscovery and engineering design.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 17:51:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 07:57:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-24"}
