-shaped\nmassless surface states (dubbed as hourglass fermions). The emergence of the\nabove exotic topological matter perfectly demonstrates the crucial roles of\nboth symmetry and topology in understanding the colorful world of quantum\nmaterials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-04"}
