 of torsion and curvature scalars near\nthe singularity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Jun 2022 18:49:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Oct 2022 15:54:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-08"}
